          "system": "5e2024",
          "resource_id": "levelled_description",
          "stats": {
            "description": {
              "value": "You gain the following benefits.\n\nAbility Score Increase. Increase your Intelligence, Wisdom, or Charisma by 1, to a maximum of 20.\n\nEnergy Mastery. Choose one of the following damage types: Acid, Cold, Fire, Lightning, or Thunder. Spells you cast ignore Resistance to damage of the chosen type. In addition, when you roll damage for a spell you cast that deals damage of that type, you can treat any 1 on a damage die as a 2.\n\nRepeatable. You can take this feat more than once, but you must choose a different damage type each time for Energy Mastery"
            },
